OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FA baby who was murdered by his
OL,8,Fadoptive father had been taken to
OL,9,Fhospital three times, was seen by a
OL,10,F"battery of professionals", and police
OL,11,Fwere even called, in the weeks before
OL,12,Fhis death.
OL,14,FJamie Varley, 37, adopted Preston
OL,15,FDavey, at nine-months-old with his
OL,16,Fpartner, ex-public schoolboy and
OL,17,Ffinancial sales manager, John McGowan-
OL,18,FFazakerley, 32.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FBut in the four months he was in their
OL,8,Fcare, Preston was routinely ill-
OL,9,Ftreated, had indecent images and
OL,10,Fvideos taken of him, and was sexually
OL,11,Fabused and physically assaulted at
OL,12,Ftheir home in Blackpool.
OL,14,FHe suffered 40 traumatic injuries
OL,15,Fbefore his death on 27 July 2023.
OL,17,FDuring an eight-week trial, Preston
OL,18,FCrown Court was told that social
OL,19,Fworkers, teachers, doctors and nurses
OL,20,Fall saw Preston, a "highly visible"
OL,21,Flooked-after child.
OL,26,@|D@TOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FA Child Safeguarding Practice Review,
OL,8,Flaunched by Oldham Council after the
OL,9,Fbaby's death, was paused during
OL,10,Fcriminal proceedings and is now
OL,11,Fexpected to recommence after the
OL,12,Ftrial, which concluded on 15 June.
OL,14,FVarley, a high school teacher, was
OL,15,Ffound guilty of murdering and sexually
OL,16,Fabusing the 13-month-old baby Preston
OL,17,Fwhen he had adopted him and treated as
OL,18,Fa "plaything".
OL,26,@zD@COUzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
