CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FOne element of the review is expected
OL,8,Fto focus on whether any opportunities
OL,9,Fwere missed in the care of Preston
OL,10,Fbefore his death.
OL,12,FBorn four weeks early, weighing 5lb
OL,13,F7oz, his mother, convicted killer
OL,14,FSarah Davey, was living at the time on
OL,15,Fthe mother and baby unit at women's
OL,16,Fprison HMP Styal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
