PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FAt five-days-old Preston was taken
OL,8,Finto emergency care by Oldham Council
OL,9,Fvia an interim care order, and placed
OL,10,Fwith foster parents, where he remained
OL,11,Ffor the first nine months of his life.
OL,13,FWhile in foster care Preston was a
OL,14,Fhappy, bubbly baby and, despite a
OL,15,Fslight reflux issue, was described as
OL,16,F"thriving".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FHigh school head of year Varley, and
OL,8,Fhis boyfriend, financial sales manager
OL,9,FMcGowan-Fazakerley, were also
OL,10,Fthriving, in their careers and in
OL,11,Ftheir relationship, and wanted to
OL,12,Fstart a family, Preston Crown Court
OL,13,Fheard.
OL,15,FThey entered the process, training
OL,16,Fpartly online because of Covid, and in
OL,17,FJanuary 2023 were approved as
OL,18,Fprospective adoptive parents by
OL,19,FAdoption Now, an organisation used by
OL,20,Flocal councils.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FAdoption Now concluded Preston Davey
OL,8,Fneeded "love, affection, safety and
OL,9,Fstability" and at his pre-adoption
OL,10,Fmedical the doctor's notes said:
OL,11,F"Absolutely gorgeous, happy, alert.
OL,12,FConstant smiles."
OL,14,FBoth Preston and the parents were
OL,15,Fassigned social workers from Oldham
OL,16,FCouncil.
OL,18,FThey began the familiarisation process
OL,19,Fwith Preston by visiting him at the
OL,20,Fhome of Sandra and Paul Cooper, the
OL,21,Ffoster parents.
OL,26,@pD@HOUqD@JO]sD@AOUtD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FMrs Cooper said she had to show the
OL,8,Fnew parents virtually everything that
OL,9,Fwas needed to look after a baby.
OL,11,FLater, Mrs Cooper called a social
OL,12,Fworker after struggling to get to see
OL,13,FPreston after his adoption, saying she
OL,14,Fhad a "gut feeling" something was
OL,15,Fwrong.
OL,26,@vD@GOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
