OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FPreston spent his first night at the
OL,8,Fdefendants' home in Blackpool on 1
OL,9,FApril and two days later was "move
OL,10,Fday" as Preston settled in with his
OL,11,Fadopted parents and their pet dog
OL,12,FMaximus.
OL,14,FWithin days problems began to emerge
OL,15,Fas the defendants learned about the
OL,16,Fsleep deprivation and "roller-coaster"
OL,17,Fof becoming new parents.
OL,26,@qD@^OUrD@DO]xD@WOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FIn the first week Varley texted his
OL,8,Fsister, a baby sleep trainer, saying:
OL,9,F"He's dead meat today. Didn't sleep
OL,10,Flast night after 11.30. Up every, one
OL,11,Fand a half hours."
OL,13,FOn the evening of 15 May, McGowan-
OL,14,FFazakerley made, then abandoned, a 999
OL,15,Fcall, and the operator only heard a
OL,16,Fvoice saying: "Put it down..."
OL,18,FThe operator returned the call but was
OL,19,Ftold the call was supposed to be to
OL,20,F111 to report Preston having
OL,21,F"breathing problems".
OL,26,@qD@AOUsD@RO]xD@OOUxD@^O]}D@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FThe next day a health visitor made a
OL,8,Fscheduled call to the house and
OL,9,FPreston was reported as appearing well.
OL,11,FAt 11.10am on 25 May, Preston was
OL,12,Ftaken to Blackpool Victoria Hospital,
OL,13,Ffor the first of three visits in three
OL,14,Fmonths.
OL,16,FFloppy and unresponsive, Varley
OL,17,Freported he had a nose bleed, seizure
OL,18,Fand breathing difficulties.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FBut paediatric sister Zoe Hellowell
OL,8,Fand Nurse Holly Edwards noticed
OL,9,Fbruising on Preston's head.
OL,11,FA medical report says Preston had
OL,12,F"unexplained injuries, inconsistent
OL,13,Fwith a version of events given..."
OL,15,FHospital safeguarding was informed and
OL,16,Fsocial services and Lancashire Police
OL,17,Fcalled.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FBut after discussion with medical
OL,8,Fstaff the bruises on a baby learning
OL,9,Fto walk were not regarded as
OL,10,Fsuspicious, a medical explanation had
OL,11,Fbeen given for the injuries, and the
OL,12,Fmatter ended there.
OL,14,FOn 30 June, Preston was back in
OL,15,Fhospital for a second time.
OL,17,FAt about 8.25pm, Varley and McGowan-
OL,18,FFazakerley took him in with a rash,
OL,19,Fdiarrhoea, vomiting and high
OL,20,Ftemperature.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FMedics again noted bruising to
OL,8,FPreston's head.
OL,10,FThey were shown a home video of
OL,11,FPreston playing and pulling a toy box
OL,12,Fon to himself, by way of explanation,
OL,13,FVarley commenting: "You lot are going
OL,14,Fto think we have been abusing him or
OL,15,Fsomething."
OL,17,FIt was only later it was discovered
OL,18,Fthe toy box video was filmed 12 days
OL,19,Fearlier, so an unlikely explanation
OL,20,Ffor the bruises.
OL,26,@uD@TOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FPreston's third visit to the same
OL,8,Fhospital came on the morning of 6 July.
OL,10,FVarley took him in for an injury to
OL,11,Fhis left arm, sustained, he said,
OL,12,Fwhile putting him in his cot the
OL,13,Fprevious evening, though he appeared
OL,14,Fto give different and inconsistent
OL,15,Fexplanations to different people.
OL,17,FAfter X-ray a cast was applied for a
OL,18,Ffractured elbow.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FThe same day the child's social
OL,8,Fworker, Amy Shepherdson, who had been
OL,9,Fin contact with the hospital, texted
OL,10,FVarley to say: "Just to reassure you
OL,11,Fthey said they had absolutely no
OL,12,Fconcerns. U absolutely did the right
OL,13,Fthing."
OL,15,FShe visited the family home, but there
OL,16,Fwere no concerns raised.
OL,18,FA day later Helen Magee, an
OL,19,Findependent reviewer from Oldham
OL,20,Fsocial services, visited Preston at
OL,21,Fhome.
OL,26,@rD@POUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FIn her report of the visit, apparently
OL,8,Faddressed to the baby, she wrote:
OL,9,F"Preston, I did watch your responses
OL,10,Fto your daddies quite carefully as I
OL,11,Fam aware that you have had a few
OL,12,Fhospital admissions of late and this
OL,13,Fmade me ponder a little as to whether
OL,14,Fthere was a problem that I couldn't
OL,15,Fsee.
OL,17,F"I decided there wasn't an issue..."
OL,26,@qD@AOUyD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FVarley had taken a year off work as
OL,8,Fhead of year, and textiles and design
OL,9,Fteacher, at South Shore Academy in
OL,10,FBlackpool.
OL,12,FHe was still in touch with colleagues,
OL,13,Fasking one to get him a prescription
OL,14,Ffor anti-depressant drugs, which she
OL,15,Fdeclined.
OL,17,FAnd in the first week of July, he made
OL,18,Fa surprise visit with Preston, arm in
OL,19,Fa cast, to fellow teacher Janet Gee.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1781722095
OL,3,CBaby seen by 'battery of
OL,4,Cprofessionals' before being murdered
OL,5,Cby adoptive dad
OL,7,FMs Gee said Varley told her he was
OL,8,Fstruggling mentally and having "dark
OL,9,Fthoughts" about drowning or
OL,10,Fsuffocating Preston.
OL,12,FLater that month Varley rushed the
OL,13,Fchild to hospital a final time,
OL,14,Fclaiming the baby had drowned in the
OL,15,Fbath.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for Adoption Now said:
OL,18,F"This was a deeply upsetting case, and
OL,19,Four thoughts are with everyone
OL,20,Faffected by these truly awful crimes.
OL,26,@pD@`OUqD@IO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/21
