OL,7,F"Adoption Now follows a strict and
OL,8,Frigorous process in line with all
OL,9,Frelevant legislation and guidance in
OL,10,Fthe assessment and approval of
OL,11,Fadopters.
OL,13,F"An independent Child Safeguarding
OL,14,FPractice Review is being completed."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Oldham Council
OL,17,Fsaid: "The death of any child is a
OL,18,Ftragedy, but this is a particularly
OL,19,Fheart-wrenching and disturbing case.
