OL,7,F"We are thankful that the perpetrators
OL,8,Fof the sickening murder and abuse of
OL,9,Fan innocent child have today been
OL,10,Fconvicted for their crimes.
OL,12,F"An independent Child Safeguarding
OL,13,FPractice Review is already under way,
OL,14,Fwhich will examine the handling of
OL,15,FPreston's safeguarding.
OL,17,F"Our thoughts remain with Preston's
OL,18,Ffamily, loved ones, and the many
OL,19,Fpeople affected by this case."
